---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /blog/
title: "Blog — Made Out of Clay Productions"
description: "Gentle, practical reads for parents and educators: neurodiversity, big feelings, bedtime, patience, and the picture books that help."
breadcrumbs:
  - { name: "Home", url: "/" }
  - { name: "Blog", url: "/blog/" }
---
<section class="page-head">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h1>The Blog</h1>
    <p>Practical, warm reads for the grown-ups raising and teaching little ones.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="wrap">
    {% if collections.posts.length %}
    <div class="post-list">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
      <article class="post-card">
        <time datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
        <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        <a href="{{ post.url }}">Read more &rarr;</a>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <p class="prose">First posts coming soon.</p>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>
